      "title": "Jaffna. Emanaka Rambutan for the boy",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 10-year-old boy, Dharmaraza Darshikan, died tragically after swallowing a rambutan seed in Kollankalatti, Kangesanthurai.",
        "The said boy was taken to Thellipappa Aadar Hospital when he was struggling to breathe after swallowing the rambutan fruit."
